<Layout title="About Quadball Canada">
  <PageHero
    title="About Us"
    subtitle="Advancing the sport of quadball in Canada since 2014."
    ctaText="Get Involved"
    ctaHref="/get-involved/"
  />
  <section style="padding: 3rem 0;">
    <h2>Our Mission</h2>
    <p>Quadball Canada is dedicated to growing and supporting the sport of quadball across the nation. We promote inclusivity, athleticism, and community through this unique sport.</p>

    <h2>Our Values</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Inclusivity and diversity in sport</li>
      <li>Fair play and sportsmanship</li>
      <li>Community building</li>
      <li>Athletic excellence</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Programs</h2>
    <p>We offer various programs to support players, teams, and communities across Canada, including national championships, development camps, and referee training.</p>
  </section>
</Layout>

